        "action": "2 Minute Silence for anti-slavery and our colonial past.",
        "additional_details": "This will serve as a reminder and a poignant event in our national calendar to recognise the oppression that was inflicted by our government and foreign policy, and a national opportunity to reflect and remember the generations affected. This could be conducted on international anti slavery day.",
